thread.title: GRIFFIN, JENNIFER

author: GRIFFIN, JENNIFER
title: GRIFFIN, JENNIFER
text: I always buy my coffee beans and any other related coffee needs here. Never had a problem. Great selection of coffee, ground or whole beans. And you can find any kind of coffee gear your budget will allow. WholeLatteLove has everything and then some and can teach you how to use it too. I have no reason to shop anywhere else.
